{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"同步","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/Synchronous","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>同步</em>（Synchronous）是指各方在接收（必要的話還會執行與回覆）訊息時，立刻（或盡可能接近立刻）執行的即時通訊。</p>\n<p>以人類通訊來比喻就是電話：在電話通訊時，你通常會立刻回覆對方的訊息。</p>\n<p>很多程式指令都是同步的：例如在計算時，環境會立刻回傳結果，除非你撰寫程式時不讓它這麼做。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"深入理解","title":"深入理解","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"技術參考","title":"技術參考","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/Asynchronous\">非同步</a></li>\n  <li>使用 <a href=\"/zh-TW_docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest\">XMLHttpRequest()</a> <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/API\">API</a> 完成 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/Synchronous_and_Asynchronous_Requests\">同步與非同步請求</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"深入理解","id":"深入理解"}],"summary":"同步（Synchronous）是指各方在接收（必要的話還會執行與回覆）訊息時，立刻（或盡可能接近立刻）執行的即時通訊。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Synchronous","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Sincrónico","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Synchrone","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Synchronous (同期通信方式)","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Síncrono","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Синхронный","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Synchronous（同步）","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/glossary/synchronous","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/glossary/synchronous/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary","title":"術語表"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/Synchronous","title":"同步"}],"pageTitle":"同步 - 術語表 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}